title: Mixtape Game: I Got Stung By Bees After Getting Pushed Over
description:
Mixtape Game hosted by Jenny w/ Special Guest E. White from the night show! // 

You are camping with ___________ (fill in the blank) for the holiday weekend.  What song is playing as you're sitting around the campfire at night and what activities are you engaging in (drinking beer, roasting marshmallows, telling ghost stories, etc.)?

You woke up the next morning and quickly realized you forgot to put bug spray on the night before, what song is playing as you scratch your mosquito bites to the point of breaking skin? 

You've recovered from the itchy mosquito bites and now are participating in the campground relay race.  You've been chosen to do the final leg for your team which is the potato sack race.  What song plays as you hop to the finish line to get the W for your team?
